data.description: Welcome Home...exclusive corner property in the heart of the desirable Packer Park community! This move in ready home offers more than 2 car parking and large detached garage. The future possibilities of creating your own custom home are endless! 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms including basement powder room, kitchen with granite counter tops, separate dining room and large deck off living area! The garage is off the deck and is standard size (12 Ft wide and 22 Ft deep) with 2 car parking in front of garage. Newly installed luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout the first and second floors and freshly painted light grey walls makes this home ready to move in! This home also features central air and whirlpool bath tub! Property being sold as is! HVAC upgraded in 2022, Roof is only 10 years old! Conveniently located near I95 & Route 76 as well as Citizens Bank Park, Wells Fargo Center & Lincoln Financial Field. Schedule your showing today!
